Necessario instalar o libreoffice : 
Need to install :
https://pt-br.libreoffice.org/donate/dl/win-x86_64/7.3.1/pt-BR/LibreOffice_7.3.1_Win_x64.msi

1 - Open project "OpenOffice_Calc.dproj"
2 - Clean
3 - Build
4 - install
5 - tools -> options -> language -> Delphi -> Library -> Library/ADD "C:\yourLocal\Component_OpenOffice_Calc\Src"

Tested Delphi version
- 10.4
- Seattle
- X8

Para uso básico de leitura e gravação de plhanilha, use apenas o componente
For basic read and write sheet usage, just use the component

Para estilizar a planilha, use as units adicionais: uOpenOfficeHelper.pas, uOpenOfficeCollors.pas 
To style the worksheet, use the additional units: uOpenOfficeHelper.pas, uOpenOfficeCollors.pas 

